Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.73,0:23:08.00,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无重力的暗阎　唯有摸索前行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.32,0:23:10.79,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS Gothic}Where do we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.61,0:23:19.37,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同莫比乌斯环一般　命运九转轮回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.37,0:23:22.20,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS Gothic\fsp0.1}Win, Lose Or Draw
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.08,0:23:28.17,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真实究竟何在{\fnMS Gothic}？ {\fsp0}Lies & Truth
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.50,0:23:34.44,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光影回转{\fsp-9}　{\fsp1.5}阴阳相生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.44,0:23:39.40,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运之骰一经掷出　就已无法停止转动
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.64,0:23:42.36,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS Gothic\fsp0}Dive into the Light
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.18,0:23:50.77,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毁灭之风扬　我只欲逆风直上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.77,0:23:53.70,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将你紧紧拥入怀抱中
